description: Golden Star Enterprises Ltd., through its subsidiary, Enigmai Ltd., provides software solutions in Israel. It offers Enigmai Business Suite, a workforce management software that enables large organizations to manage their employees' schedules and save money. The company was formerly known as Terralene Fuels Corporation and changed its name to Golden Star Enterprises Ltd. in July 2013. Golden Star Enterprises Ltd. was incorporated in 1993 and is based in Claymont, Delaware.
